"time":162200,"text":"this too shall pass"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168040,"text":"If there ain't\nall that much to lug around,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":171200,"text":"you can't keep letting it get you down --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":174440,"text":"this too shall pass"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178920,"text":"When the morning comes --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180760,"text":"you can't keep letting it get you down,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":183040,"text":"no you can't keep letting it"}]},{"cues":[{"time":184920,"text":"When the morning comes --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":186680,"text":"you can't keep letting it get you down,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":189080,"text":"no you can't keep letting it"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190960,"text":"When the morning comes --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":192800,"text":"you can't keep letting it get you down,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":195080,"text":"no you can't keep letting it"}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"When the morning comes --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":198880,"text":"you can't keep letting it get you down,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":201120,"text":"no you can't keep letting it"}]},{"cues":[{"time":203000,"text":"When the morning comes"}]},{"cues":[{"time":210600,"text":"(Paint guns fire)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":212080,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":220720,"text":"Damian Kulash:\nThank you, thanks very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222800,"text":"We are OK Go,"},{"time":224680,"text":"and we've been together\nas a band since 1998."},{"time":228440,"text":"But in the last decade,"},{"time":229720,"text":"we've become known as much\nfor the elaborate music videos,"},{"time":232760,"text":"like the one we just saw,"},{"time":234040,"text":"as for the songs they accompany."},{"time":236680,"text":"So we will play along with another\none of those in a few minutes,"},{"time":239800,"text":"but in the meantime,"},{"time":241040,"text":"we want to address this question\nthat we get asked all the time"},{"time":244400,"text":"but we've really never come up\nwith an adequate answer for it,"},{"time":247400,"text":"and that is, how do we\nthink of those ideas?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":251400,"text":"The videos are not all\nRube Goldberg machines, by the way."},{"time":254160,"text":"Last year we did a dance in zero gravity,"},{"time":256279,"text":"and once we set up an obstacle course"},{"time":260079,"text":"out of thousands of musical\ninstruments in the desert,"},{"time":262840,"text":"and then played them\nby stunt driving a car through them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265560,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":266600,"text":"For one of the videos,"},{"time":267880,"text":"we choreographed\nhundreds of people with umbrellas"},{"time":270280,"text":"in an abandoned parking lot outside Tokyo,"},{"time":272680,"text":"and then filmed them from a drone\na half a mile in the air."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276520,"text":"So it's all of these ideas\nthat people are curious about,"},{"time":280160,"text":"and the reason we've had so much trouble\ndescribing how we think of these ideas"},{"time":284440,"text":"is that it doesn't really feel\nlike we think of them at all."},{"time":288400,"text":"It feels like we find them."},{"time":291960,"text":"And by way of explanation --"},{"time":293880,"text":"well, I have a compulsive habit."},{"time":297080,"text":"I play parallax and perspective games\nwith my eyes pretty much all the time,"},{"time":302160,"text":"and it's something I've been doing\nsince I was a teenager."},{"time":304920,"text":"And I think the big contributing\nfactor may have been"},{"time":307680,"text":"that this is how I decorated\nmy high school bedroom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":311920,"text":"And being a teenager,"},{"time":313200,"text":"what I did in there, of course,\nwas just talk on the phone"},{"time":315960,"text":"for staggering amounts of time."},{"time":319160,"text":"So I was in this visual maelstrom"},{"time":321560,"text":"just pretty much\nusually sitting in one place,"},{"time":323760,"text":"and I guess just\nthe overload in general --"},{"time":326560,"text":"my brain kind of tried\nto make sense of it, and I would --"},{"time":329760,"text":"If I could move my head off\nto one side a little bit,"},{"time":332280,"text":"the edge of the desk\nwould line up just perfectly"},{"time":334640,"text":"with that poster on the opposite wall;"},{"time":336480,"text":"or if I put my thumb out,"},{"time":337760,"text":"I could close first my left eye\nand then my right,"},{"time":340160,"text":"and my thumb would bounce back and forth"},{"time":342120,"text":"between Jimi Hendrix's\nleft eye and his right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":345560,"text":"It was not a conscious thing, of course,"},{"time":347920,"text":"this is just kind of the equivalent\nof doodling while you're talking,"},{"time":351200,"text":"and it's still something\nI do all the time."},{"time":353320,"text":"This is my wife, Kristin --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":354680,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":355880,"text":"Yeah!"},{"time":357360,"text":"Woo!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":359400,"text":"And it's not uncommon\nthat we are out at dinner,"},{"time":362920,"text":"and in the middle of a great conversation\nshe'll just stop mid-sentence,"},{"time":366360,"text":"and when she stops is when I realize\nthat I'm the one who's acting weird"},{"time":369800,"text":"because I'm like bobbing and weaving."},{"time":371640,"text":"And what I'm trying to do\nis get that ficus back there"},{"time":374240,"text":"to stick out of her head like a ponytail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":378600,"text":"The point of telling you\nall this is that --"},{"time":381520,"text":"for me this is what it feels like\nto have an idea."},{"time":383920,"text":"It's like they're made\nof these disparate parts,"},{"time":387480,"text":"these disparate chunks\nsort of floating out there."},{"time":389880,"text":"And if you're receptive\nand you're observant,"},{"time":392960,"text":"and crucially, if you're\nin exactly the right place,"},{"time":395560,"text":"you can get them to just line up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398440,"text":"So if you get used to --"},{"time":399720,"text":"if it's your job\nto think of ideas this way,"},{"time":402280,"text":"they'll start beckoning to you"},{"time":404560,"text":"the way that Jimi's eyes\nbeckoned from that poster,"},{"time":407000,"text":"or the ficus beckons\nfrom behind Kristin's head."},{"time":409640,"text":"Writing music feels like that process\njust over and over again,"},{"time":412640,"text":"like you've got a bunch of sounds\nor a groove or a chord progression"},{"time":417040,"text":"and you're just looking\nfor that thing on the other side,"},{"time":419760,"text":"that little chunk over there,\nthat puzzle piece that clicks right in."},{"time":423360,"text":"And when it does click,"},{"time":424720,"text":"it doesn't feel like you\nthought up that puzzle piece,"},{"time":427400,"text":"it feels like you found it --"},{"time":429080,"text":"like it was a set of relationships\nthat you unlocked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433760,"text":"But with the videos in particular,"},{"time":436400,"text":"we're usually looking\nfor this specific feeling"},{"time":438640,"text":"which is wonder."},{"time":439920,"text":"And there's always a component\nof surprise to wonder,"},{"time":442840,"text":"so we're not just looking for good ideas,"},{"time":445200,"text":"we're looking for good ideas\nthat surprise us in some way."},{"time":448440,"text":"And this causes something of a problem,"},{"time":450680,"text":"because ..."},{"time":453240,"text":"the process that we all use to make stuff,"},{"time":455680,"text":"it actually has a very strong bias\nagainst surprising ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":459240,"text":"The process I'm talking about\nis the one you all know --"},{"time":461920,"text":"we all do it all the time."},{"time":463200,"text":"You think of an idea."},{"time":464640,"text":"You just sit and think\nof your brilliant idea"},{"time":466800,"text":"and then you come up with a plan"},{"time":468400,"text":"for how you're going to make\nthat idea happen."},{"time":470600,"text":"And then with that plan in mind,"},{"time":472200,"text":"you go back and double-check\nyour original idea"},{"time":474440,"text":"and maybe revise it,"},{"time":475720,"text":"and then bouncing back and forth\nbetween the idea and the plan,"},{"time":478720,"text":"the plan and the idea,"},{"time":479960,"text":"eventually you come up\nwith a truly great plan."},{"time":482200,"text":"And then once you have that,\nand only then,"},{"time":484280,"text":"do you go out and you execute."},{"time":486440,"text":"And this is like --"},{"time":488120,"text":"this is sort of a flawless system"},{"time":490440,"text":"in terms of maximizing your resources,"},{"time":492440,"text":"because this -- super cheap."},{"time":495600,"text":"Thinking usually costs very little,"},{"time":497320,"text":"but this is really expensive\nmost of the time,"},{"time":499520,"text":"so by the time you get there,"},{"time":500960,"text":"you want to make sure\nyou're super prepared"},{"time":503040,"text":"and you can squeeze every last drop\nout of what you've got."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505880,"text":"But there are problems with this,"},{"time":507520,"text":"and math will help us\nreveal the biggest one."},{"time":510880,"text":"Go back to that video\nthat we just showed you."},{"time":513440,"text":"That Rube Goldberg machine,"},{"time":515200,"text":"it had about 130 interactions in it."},{"time":517520,"text":"That was 130 things"},{"time":520200,"text":"that we had to have go\naccording to our plan."},{"time":523039,"text":"So let's assume that we want\nto make a new video now,"},{"time":526920,"text":"similarly complex -- 130 moving parts."},{"time":530800,"text":"If we're really good planners\nin that system,"},{"time":533360,"text":"it seems like maybe\nwe could be good enough"},{"time":536640,"text":"to get every part of that system\nto be 90 percent reliable."},{"time":541320,"text":"90 percent sounds good, right?"},{"time":542800,"text":"Well, it's not."},{"time":544080,"text":"It's terrible actually.\nThe numbers say so."},{"time":546400,"text":"The chance of getting all 130 things\nto not fail at the same time"},{"time":551160,"text":"is .9 for 90 percent to the 130th power."},{"time":554440,"text":"So calculate that out and you get ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556360,"text":"(Ding)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":557920,"text":".000001,"},{"time":563520,"text":"which is one ten-thousandth\nof one percent,"},{"time":566000,"text":"so your chance for success\nis literally one in a million."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569800,"text":"(Whistle)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":571440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":573160,"text":"I mean that's not a gamble I want to take,"},{"time":575640,"text":"so let's ratchet up\nthat reliability to 99 percent."},{"time":579640,"text":".99 to the 130th power is ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582520,"text":"(Ding)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583680,"text":".27 -- 27 percent."},{"time":585640,"text":"Significantly less daunting --"},{"time":587240,"text":"like this might even be usable."},{"time":588760,"text":"But really think about that."},{"time":590160,"text":"How many parts of your lives\nare 99 percent reliable?"},{"time":594520,"text":"And could you really get 130 of them\nall in one place at once?"},{"time":599200,"text":"And if you really could,"},{"time":601520,"text":"doesn't it seem\nlike you deserve to succeed?"},{"time":604000,"text":"Like that is --"},{"time":605520,"text":"that thing is going to work, right?"},{"time":607240,"text":"But no, it actually fails three times\nmore often than it succeeds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610680,"text":"So the upshot of all this"},{"time":612400,"text":"is that if your project\nis pretty complex --"},{"time":615640,"text":"like, you know,\nevery ambitious project is --"},{"time":618760,"text":"if you've got a lot of moving parts,"},{"time":620520,"text":"you're basically constrained\nto just reshuffling ideas"},{"time":624160,"text":"that have already demonstrably\nproven that they're 100 percent reliable."},{"time":629040,"text":"So now go back to me sitting\nwith my thumb in the air"},{"time":631560,"text":"trying to line up something surprising."},{"time":633640,"text":"If the only things I'm allowed\nto consider in the first place"},{"time":636760,"text":"are ideas that have already been done\nover and over and over again,"},{"time":640880,"text":"I am screwed."},{"time":644000,"text":"However, there are ways around this,"},{"time":645760,"text":"because we all know that there are\ntons of untried ideas still out there,"},{"time":650200,"text":"and plenty of them will turn out\nto be every bit as reliable as we need,"},{"time":653880,"text":"it's just that we don't yet know\nthey are reliable"},{"time":656280,"text":"when we are at this planning phase."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658240,"text":"So what we do is we try\nto identify some place"},{"time":661960,"text":"where there might just be\na ton of those untried ideas."},{"time":665160,"text":"We try to find a sandbox"},{"time":667400,"text":"and then we gamble\na whole bunch of our resources"},{"time":669960,"text":"on getting in that sandbox and playing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":672800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":674440,"text":"Because we have to trust\nthat it's the process in the sandbox"},{"time":677480,"text":"that will reveal to us\nwhich ideas are not only surprising,"},{"time":681360,"text":"but surprisingly reliable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":683600,"text":"So some of the sandboxes\nthat we've started videos with."},{"time":686640,"text":"Let's play with optical illusions."},{"time":690200,"text":"Let's try to dance on moving surfaces."},{"time":692720,"text":"Let's try to make toast\nwith a laser cutter."},{"time":696200,"text":"Or let's do something in one\nof those zero-gravity airplanes."},{"time":701400,"text":"But then instead\nof actually trying to sit there"},{"time":703680,"text":"and think out what that something is,"},{"time":705520,"text":"we spent a full third of our budget\ngetting in an actual Vomit Comet"},{"time":709480,"text":"and bouncing off the walls for a week."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712200,"text":"So this may seem to you like testing,"},{"time":716120,"text":"but it really isn't,"},{"time":717760,"text":"because at this point\nwe don't yet know what our idea is,"},{"time":720720,"text":"we don't have a plan to be testing."},{"time":723480,"text":"So we're just --"},{"time":725000,"text":"we're just playing,"},{"time":726240,"text":"we're just trying everything\nwe can think of,"},{"time":728400,"text":"because we need to get this idea space\nfilled up with a chaos"},{"time":732520,"text":"like the one in my high school bedroom."},{"time":734680,"text":"Because then, if we can\ndo the bob and weave thing,"},{"time":737640,"text":"if we can put our thumbs up\nand get just a few things to line up --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":741680,"text":"(Ding)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":742920,"text":"chances are no one else has ever made\nthose same things line up before."},{"time":747280,"text":"And when we're done with that project,"},{"time":749120,"text":"people will ask us again\nhow we thought of that idea,"},{"time":751640,"text":"and we'll be stumped,\nbecause from our perspective,"},{"time":754080,"text":"it doesn't feel like\nwe thought of it at all,"},{"time":756240,"text":"it just feels like we found it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":757800,"text":"So we'll play another video for you now\nand the song along with it."},{"time":761000,"text":"This is for the song \"The One Moment,\""},{"time":762880,"text":"and for this one,\nthe sandbox was ballistics and math."},{"time":767240,"text":"So I spent a full month putting together\na giant spreadsheet for this."},{"time":772720,"text":"It was like my playspace\nwas 400 lines long"},{"time":775880,"text":"and 25 columns wide --"},{"time":778600,"text":"which I presume that if anybody is going\nto understand that, it's this crowd."}]},{"cues":[{"time":782240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":783520,"text":"Nothing is better\nthan a giant spreadsheet, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":785920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":787160,"text":"Well, thank you everyone, very much."},{"time":788920,"text":"We are OK Go,"},{"time":790160,"text":"and this is called \"The One Moment.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":791920,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":795920,"text":"[The One Moment]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":798040,"text":"(Explosions)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":804200,"text":"[What you just saw was real"},{"time":806480,"text":"and it took 4.2 seconds]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":807760,"text":"(Video) Let me know when it's safe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":810586,"text":"(Percussion)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":811760,"text":"[Here's the same moment ..."},{"time":814360,"text":"slowed down.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":816440,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":822120,"text":"(Guitar)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":845240,"text":"(Singing) You're right,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":848200,"text":"there's nothing more lovely,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":852000,"text":"there's nothing more profound"},{"time":856360,"text":"than the certainty,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":858280,"text":"than the certainty\nthat all of this will end"}]},{"cues":[{"time":867520,"text":"That all of this will end"}]},{"cues":[{"time":872320,"text":"So open your arms to me,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":874560,"text":"open your arms to me"}]},{"cues":[{"time":876280,"text":"And this will be\nthe one moment that matters,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":879920,"text":"and this will be\nthe one thing we remember,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":883680,"text":"and this will be\nthe reason to have been here,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":887600,"text":"and this will be\nthe one moment that matters --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":891680,"text":"Oh ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":893120,"text":"(Guitar)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":899280,"text":"(Singing) So while the mud\nreclaims our footprints,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":906160,"text":"and while our bones keep looking back"}]},{"cues":[{"time":910040,"text":"at the overgrowth\nthat's swallowing the path --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":913920,"text":"but for the grace of God go we,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":917760,"text":"but for the grace of God go we"}]},{"cues":[{"time":921680,"text":"But for the grace of time and chance\nand entropy's cruel hands --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":926480,"text":"So open your arms to me,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":928640,"text":"open your arms to me"}]},{"cues":[{"time":930480,"text":"And this will be\nthe one moment that matters,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":934080,"text":"and this will be\nthe one thing we remember,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":937960,"text":"and this will be\nthe reason to have been here,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":941800,"text":"and this will be\nthe one moment that matters"}]},{"cues":[{"time":945840,"text":"Oh ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":949160,"text":"So won't you stay here with me"}]},{"cues":[{"time":951720,"text":"and we'll build\n'til we've blistered our hands"}]},{"cues":[{"time":957000,"text":"So won't you stay here with me\nand we'll build us some temples,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":961600,"text":"build us some castles,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":963600,"text":"build us some monuments"}]},{"cues":[{"time":965280,"text":"and burn them all right down"}]},{"cues":[{"time":968000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":978720,"text":"(Singing) So open your arms to me"}]},{"cues":[{"time":982680,"text":"And this will be\nthe one moment that matters,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":986280,"text":"and this will be\nthe reason to have been here,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":990200,"text":"and this will be\nthe one thing we remember,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":994040,"text":"and this will be\nthe one moment that matters"}]},{"cues":[{"time":998200,"text":"So won't you stay here with me,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1000120,"text":"we'll build 'til we blister our hands"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002400,"text":"And this will be\nthe one moment that matters --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1005560,"text":"So won't you stay here with me\nand build us some temples --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1010040,"text":"This will be the one\nmoment that matters --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014000,"text":"Build us some temples --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1015600,"text":"The one moment that matters --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1017480,"text":"Build us some monuments --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1019480,"text":"The one moment that matters"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1021520,"text":"Build us some temples --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1023320,"text":"The one moment that matters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1025560,"text":"Build us some monuments --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1027040,"text":"The one moment that matters, oh"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1029920,"text":"(Guitar)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1034960,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}